data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!!! This stunning home is situated in the highly sought-after area of College Park. The entire interior has been recently painted, and new pool supplies were added in 2022, along with a new fence. The house boasts a spacious master bedroom complete with a walk-in closet and a generously sized bathroom featuring double sinks. Additionally, there are three other well-proportioned bedrooms and extra rooms that can serve as a game room or a movie room. A new water heater in Oct 2023.
